TokenInfo_Description1="Tether, also commonly referred to as <a href='https://tether.to/en/' class='a-config' target='_blank'>USDT</a>, is a popular stablecoin often used by investors who want to avoid volatility while holding funds within the cryptocurrency ecosystem. Much like the other popular stablecoin, USD Coin, more commonly known as USDC, USDT is also native to the internet and can be used similarly - holding in crypto wallets, making purchases, trading, etc. Since USDT is pegged to a traditional FIAT currency, it’s often backed by collateralized reserves made entirely or mostly of the pegged currency to avoid volatility of value.<br><br>Our cross-chain bridge, cBridge, supports the cross-chain bridging of USDT <span><img class='describe-img' src='https://get.celer.app/cbridge-icons/USDT.png' alt=''/></span> between multiple chains with the fastest speeds, lowest costs, and most secure transactions available. The full name of this asset is Tether and the ticker of this asset is USDT."


