Chain_Info2_Description="Aptos has roots closely stemming from the Diem blockchain initiative where it was introduced and later abandoned from Meta. With many of the original key developers working on building Aptos, the focus has remained the same—delivering a L1 that’s scalable, reliable, and secure for the masses. This is possible by using a RUST based programming language, MOVE, which has been gaining traction with newer blockchain entrants including Sui. Aptos is committed to growing their ecosystem by onboarding several core ecosystem applications, including working with key interoperability providers such as Celer Network in bridging assets, NFTs, and general message passing. APTOS (or APT) is the native token of Aptos, where the gas amount is determined by instructions, storage, and payload."
