Chain_Info2_Token_Description1="APTOS is the native token of the Aptos blockchain, where the gas amount is determined by instructions, storage, and payload. APT can be used to (1) pay for network transactions, (2) participate in network consensus via validator staking, and (3) participate in on-chain governance voting. <br><br>The APT token also has a few unique characteristics such as having a standardized implementation which improves interoperability and compatibility across the Aptos ecosystem, while facilitating the ability to have liquidity to be easily stored, transferred, and exchanged. This is achieved by defining fungible, semi-fungible and non-fungible tokens in a single smart contract. APT token properties enable users to customize and define the parameters of their own token properties.<br><br>Our cross-chain bridge, cBridge, supports the cross-chain bridging of APT <span><img class='describe-img' src='https://get.celer.app/cbridge-icons/chain-icon/aptos.png' alt=''/></span> between multiple chains with the fastest speeds, lowest costs, and most secure transactions available. The full name of this asset is APTOS and the ticker of this asset is APT."
